.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B \-\-initial\-host\-ocpu\-count [float]
.UNINDENT
.sp
The initial OCPU count of the SDDC’s ESXi hosts.
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B \-\-initial\-host\-shape\-name [text]
.UNINDENT
.sp
The initial compute shape of the SDDC’s ESXi hosts. \fI\%ListSupportedHostShapes\fP <\fBhttps://docs.cloud.oracle.com/api/#/en/vmware/20200501/SupportedHostShapes/ListSupportedHostShapes\fP>\&.
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B \-\-initial\-sku [text]
.UNINDENT
.sp
The billing option selected during SDDC creation. \fI\%ListSupportedSkus\fP <\fBhttps://docs.cloud.oracle.com/api/#/en/vmware/20200501/SupportedSkuSummary/ListSupportedSkus\fP>\&.
.sp
Accepted values are:
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
