.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B \-\-is\-hcx\-enterprise\-enabled [boolean]
.UNINDENT
.sp
Indicates whether to enable HCX Enterprise for this SDDC.
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B \-\-is\-shielded\-instance\-enabled [boolean]
.UNINDENT
.sp
Indicates whether shielded instance is enabled for this SDDC.
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B \-\-is\-single\-host\-sddc [boolean]
.UNINDENT
.sp
Indicates whether this SDDC is designated for only single ESXi host.
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B \-\-max\-wait\-seconds [integer]
.UNINDENT
.sp
The maximum time to wait for the work request to reach the state defined by \fB\-\-wait\-for\-state\fP\&. Defaults to 1200 seconds.
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B \-\-provisioning\-vlan\-id [text]
.UNINDENT
.sp
